'''Takasago Shrine''' (高砂神社) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}}.
* {{ill|Takasago Shrine (Sendai)|ja|高砂神社 (仙台市)}} – Located in {{ill|Miyagi Prefecture|ja|宮城県}}, {{ill|Sendai|ja|仙台市}}, {{ill|Miyagino-ku|ja|宮城野区}}. * {{ill|Takasago Shrine (Adachi)|ja|高砂神社 (足立区)}} – Located in {{ill|Tokyo Metropolis|ja|東京都}}, {{ill|Adachi, Tokyo|ja|足立区}}, {{ill|Adachi (Adachi-ku)|ja|足立 (足立区)}}. * {{ill|Takasago Shrine (Osaka)|ja|高砂神社 (大阪市)}} – Located in {{ill|Osaka Prefecture|ja|大阪府}}, {{ill|Osaka|ja|大阪市}}, {{ill|Suminoe-ku|ja|住之江区}}. * {{ill|Takasago Shrine (Hyogo)|ja|高砂神社}} – Located in {{ill|Hyogo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県}}, {{ill|Takasago, Hyogo|ja|高砂市}}.
